Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:45.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 小花火戴耳環了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:48.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這個是耳飾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣 沒有打耳洞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕疼所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人慾火中燒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:06.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 別看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:13.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,騙你的 沒在看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是大膽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:20.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:24.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作為賠罪跟我去賓館吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 為了獎勵跟我去賓館吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼亂七八糟的 不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 節奏都被打亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 去賓館啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:40.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 賓館賓館的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你就只會說這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你腦子裡就只想著做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是男人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:49.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不能算理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:51.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以算哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看性慾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就想和你#$*&%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:03.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是太過著急的話……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}正好我也來了興致
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 明明就說過慢慢來也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:12.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 等著我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:15.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 有人叫我去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:18.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:22.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我做的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:31.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服會拉長的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:40.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是我想看的電影 說不定會很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:43.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 好想牽住你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但現在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你會回頭看我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:00.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:02.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這就很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人也沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:13.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 明明是想看的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,卻完全看不進去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:23.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為現在真的就像是和麥兩人獨處一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在電影院裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,離得這麼近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:30.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H95&\fn@方正准圆_GBK\t(0,600,\alpha&H00&)\bord0\fs85\frz270\pos(336,521)}我愛你！至死不渝！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fn@方正准圆_GBK\bord0\fs85\pos(321.333,610.333)}我從未知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fn@方正准圆_GBK\bord0\fs85\pos(337.333,547)}戀愛成真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.49,Kuzu_text,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fn@方正准圆_GBK\bord0\fs85\pos(394.333,486.333)}是一件如此幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.54,Kuzu_text,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼無法實現的戀愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有不幸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:47.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的喜歡是「即使這樣也可以」的喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:52.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛就算無法實現也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不過是自欺欺人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是happy end的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:02.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還挺有趣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼說太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:16.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我想看的電影嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:19.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是很無聊的話會感覺對不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:22.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算很無聊的話 那也是電影的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:25.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可不用在意那種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜 喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:33.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥對剛才的事會怎麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:35.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 麥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:42.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是牽著手一起入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像就會做同一個夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:47.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,…什麼的 想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:55.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 現在簡直就像做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:56.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:59.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了我們去吃點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:02.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 夢還沒有醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:03.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:20.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那個時候我會叫住他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓我做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:34.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可悲地死纏爛打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最後還是讓他走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:44.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那只是意氣用事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:46.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,並沒有得到什麼好感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:51.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有的僅僅是欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為現在的我已經
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:59.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,連這二者的區別都無法理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:03.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓人留戀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓人著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會付出任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會讓人奪走任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不平等才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誰 不管是誰都好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:18.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我覺得自己是有價值的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:20.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何時我已變得這麼「女人」了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最初也只是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:28.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想像那樣和喜歡的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:33.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:36.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,完全無法讓心滿足呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥 好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:40.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:43.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接也沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:53.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不用在意我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:56.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:02.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快笑 今天不是很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是已經滿足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不保持笑臉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:07.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:15.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為發覺一切是夢的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:17.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,夢就會不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:20.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算晚上也很悶熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你今天陪我到這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:27.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥 我很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:29.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:31.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在中途就意識到真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 既然怎樣都實現不了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要留下快樂的回憶就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:41.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,製造出完美的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一直一直
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:44.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷循環重複就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:48.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:51.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:52.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還問什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:56.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺你剛才開始就完全不看我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:59.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我犯了不得了的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是碰到手的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:05.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被拒絕了的話 我就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:10.19,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一生都不需要真正的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:08.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂 你到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}最可 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:13.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥 今天我很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:15.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:19.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這會成為我一生的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:26.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要沉睡在不會醒的夢裡就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要孤身一人的話就能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:34.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話…我…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就會很幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:42.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:51.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 王子大人的吻打碎了夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:56.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,公主孤身一人在黑暗中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:57.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不再哭得聲嘶力竭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:03.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是因為不論悲傷還是喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都還未曾知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:08.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有想見的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:14.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想要男的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,見不到小繪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:20.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友 我沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:25.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也罷 偶爾也想一個人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:36.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥的房間 好久沒來了呢 多久了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:38.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好聞的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,約會 並不開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:46.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:47.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:51.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也有與快樂同等的不滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明知為何 卻裝作不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:12:59.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:00.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:01.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:05.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清楚 我早就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:13.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那晚安呢 乃莉子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 晚安媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:18.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,神大人 拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天能與麥一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,住在凡爾賽宮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:29.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要 我更喜歡姬路城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相比王子 武士更適合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真想快點長鬍子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在遊戲會上演王子殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:40.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒興趣呢 演樹就好了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:44.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,樹真好呢 真想演一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:50.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 麥要和我在英國啊法國一起度蜜月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不行了 我們不合適
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:57.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說組合解散了 雖然我不記得我們有拍檔過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:04.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦啊啦 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:06.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乖啦乖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:11.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起啦 別哭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不會解散啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:14.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥 喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:20.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒輒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:27.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我知道的 我是能被允許的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:31.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一旦哭泣 沒有大人不感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我其實是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:40.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不是圖書中那純粹的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:42.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一直都意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有這種自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,並且加以利用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要再裝可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很害怕伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:56.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該是更坦率地喜歡麥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他是別人的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不能做比這個更超過的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:05.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道了這才是真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:08.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不就和敷衍著去戀愛的人一樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的喜歡他的話就應該就此打住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.83,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個呢才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:17.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都不知道的是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:21.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不就此停止而回頭的話 就只會在這半吊子的感情中結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:22.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 我想觸碰他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:38.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再早點這樣做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:42.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然 並不是說剛才的事隨便怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:46.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在能和喜歡的人像這樣在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:50.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我意識到沒有比這更想得到的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:53.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這酥麻的感覺 這熱度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:57.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有現在你是只屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:59.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如此甜蜜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:03.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦知曉了就無法回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:08.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事也和她做過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 不喜歡嗎 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:16.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是 雖然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在最可真的是可愛得無法言語
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:21.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:30.26,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即使得不到你的喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:33.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能因為很可愛 而繼續活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:36.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:38.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要回應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:50.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,流星什麼的 有生以來第一次看見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以稍微許了個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正卡通_GBK\bord0\c&H2C333B&\frz288.9\pos(888,360)}中獎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:57.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個要是一擊即中的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:16:59.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就拿出勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:12.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就連不知道她想法這點也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要繼續嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:21.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,並不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:36.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這種情況下非常卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:40.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不確認一下就不能繼續的這點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:43.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:45.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 要怎麼脫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:50.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個 不把絲帶摘下來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 這種類型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:54.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「呀」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:17:59.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:02.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:05.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,胸…胸部不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:06.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不會比較？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不會比較啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是最可的 所以想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:18.54,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我會下地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:28.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我摸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:34.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:36.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為太黑了看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看不見就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:42.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣是不對的 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:44.78,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:48.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:50.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不汙染她是為了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:53.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,藕斷絲連也是為了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:57.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使如此我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很珍惜最可的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的 那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在麥心中我是十分特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:16.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,特別的不能侵犯的無法觸摸的裝飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:21.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我很希望你觸摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:24.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟蹋我也好 弄髒我也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:28.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想和麥活在同一個世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:33.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是無法實現的話 那種「特別」也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:40.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:45.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不需要 明明起不了任何作用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:47.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不需要也無法拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,執著的證明？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:55.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是 只有這些是至今為止支撐著我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:57.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,曾是寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經 不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:24.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:25.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:30.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒意識到是誰說出來想要見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:33.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但雙方終於鼓足勇氣說了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:40.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定了 在暑假結束前好好地做出告白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:42.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:47.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 在暑假結束的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:51.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,決定兩個人都能乾脆俐落地分手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:57.99,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後能夠成為真正的戀人 手牽手地去約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:03.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,早點這樣做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:05.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花掉太多時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:08.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 雖然根本就是以卵擊石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 也是太自以為是了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:19.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對於未來的事情 雖然還什麼也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
